-----------------------------Network configuration file---------------------
Network configuration file

cd /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ for my case it is ifcfg-eno16780032

HWADDR=00:50:56:AA:C9:98
TYPE=Ethernet
BOOTPROTO=dhcp
DEFROUTE=yes
PEERDNS=yes
PEERROUTES=yes
IPV4_FAILURE_FATAL=no
IPV6INIT=yes
IPV6_AUTOCONF=yes
IPV6_DEFROUTE=yes
IPV6_PEERDNS=yes
IPV6_PEERROUTES=yes
IPV6_FAILURE_FATAL=no
NAME=eno16780032
UUID=28f5f63d-3d65-4ffa-934a-bbb63e27d884
ONBOOT=no


for manual settings 

BOOTPROTO=none
ONBOOT=yes
PREFIX=24
IPADDR=10.0.0.0.17


after configuration 
nmcli c reload

network manager  nmtui

nmcli con show 

nmcli general status

nmcli con edit



